==International broadcast==
In Canada, &quot;The Brak Show&quot; previously aired on Teletoon&#x27;s Teletoon at Night block, and currently airs on the Canadian version of Adult Swim.

==Home releases==
The first 14 episodes were released on DVD on February 1, 2005, and the remaining episodes were released on August 8, 2006. In addition to being available on DVD, &quot;The Brak Show&quot; is also available on iTunes. The series was made available on HBO Max on September 1, 2020. 

